Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上存在着肉眼无法看见的黑暗住人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.05,0:00:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们偶尔也会显露獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.03,0:00:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.69,0:01:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是为从它们手中保护你们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从地狱深渊前来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.56,0:01:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义使者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…也说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想跟鵺野老师一起滑冰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连续劈人魔!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最强情侣爱的大追击!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说又有歹徒出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 歹徒?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是传闻说出现在童守町的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这一次的被害者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是被像锐利的虎爪一样的凶器所伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且已经连续四天了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说遭到袭击的全都是情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被害者背上的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来就像是阿鵺老师的鬼手撕裂的一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不可能做出这种伤害别人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此你就去解决劈人魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是老师不是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:03:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个话题到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歹徒会出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们赶快回家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 是绝对不会碰到歹徒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为歹徒袭击的是那些很亲热的情侣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金田 你没有女朋友所以可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.68,0:04:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中岛 你胆敢说...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的妖怪 你想杀了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想吓吓你而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你找我到底有什么事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们住在同一个镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你却从来没有来看过我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是好想见你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不是妖怪就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是星期六
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午到我打工的滑冰场来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 你们大家也来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也可以去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鵺 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 反正又不用钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事情要忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在滑冰场当滑冰教练啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女她真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像奥运选手一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她是雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不是人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么对雪女这么冷淡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 我们一起滑好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去快去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟鵺野老师双人滑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们两个人的心就可以合而为一了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度滑冰?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像奥运选手一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才已经说过同样的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鵺不愧是体育系毕业的 真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 我们一起滑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢自己一个人随心所欲的滑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我求求你 请你停下来好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要罗罗嗦嗦的好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才叫你停下来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为在滑冰场上就\N可以跟老师成为亲热的一对了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小广...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乡子...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你们真大胆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为小广那家伙以前没有滑过冰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么滑的地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕他们两个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她融化掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一个人滑得很烂那就有机可乘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都很会滑的话根本就没有机会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只好让鵺野老师变成滑冰白痴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啦 鵺野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的滑冰技术真烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我教你滑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生时代被称为滑冰小鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银盘贵公子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰上天鹅的我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会滑不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会滑就不会滑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说你是像在河里溺水的野猪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是在火热的烤盘上到处翻滚的蚯蚓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:09:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我看干脆让我贴身教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵺野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要躲着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前不就说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我 寿命以及生长环境都相差太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢我 我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我们两个之间的障碍实在是太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我没有办法接受你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女的体温一上升就必须用雪人来冷却一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.33,0:09:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你刚才说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次说到重要的事情你就会变成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有歹徒 有歹徒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁快来帮我叫救护车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:10:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是人类能造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 有我陪着...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个小鬼竟然也敢泡妞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到亲亲热热的人我就一肚子火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小广 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股妖气是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小广
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可以死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.58,0:12:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这点...好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是一点点小伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鵺 快去捉犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小广就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵺野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 要是我没有穿这双滑冰鞋就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 先别急着脱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:12:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两个人一起去追他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 他在马路上滑冰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为逃得掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 他怎么可能在马路上滑冰嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女 转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女 弄跳台来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:13:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓好 要跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊 终于跟鵺野老师一起滑冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且竟然还是像这样子两颗心结合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然是为了跟鵺野老师结合而诞生的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会连这样都可以过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.07,0:15:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在我的面前这么亲热
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然是个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你退到旁边去 雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前是很幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了一个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的主人给夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.68,0:16:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以后的我就...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨那个夺走我主人的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:17:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我痛恨相爱的人 也痛恨爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 就算你被人类给抛弃也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但再怎么说也不能...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把爱情那种甜蜜的脱离现实的感觉统统消除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 你根本什么也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.10,0:17:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱情才不是你想的那么天真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我因为是雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不管我再怎么喜欢作为人类的鵺野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么喜欢他都...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲亲热热的家伙 我决饶不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印在我左手的恶鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是一味叹息自己的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而对人类的幸福怀恨在心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪大恶极的妖怪心魔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.73,0:18:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵺野...老师...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我不会再让你孤孤单单的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动物也会怀有怨恨 有时也会变成妖怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要好好疼爱它们才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小广 你的伤怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是很阵阵刺痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又痛了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以乡子你要是有空常来看我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.81,0:19:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你也未免想得太美了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你早就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号外 号外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是这个月的学校新闻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.94,0:20:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿鵺这么大一张照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊 好酷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 阿鵺也请
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪组合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}(大功劳 妖怪组合)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这两个人要怎么说才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定他们是很相配的一对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很相配的一对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.36,0:20:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们的爱情够强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天一定可以结合在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再邀请鵺野老师去游乐场玩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 阿鵺以前的老师是这么漂亮温柔的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 她是我最尊敬的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你一定很憧憬她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能够改变一次过去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.70,0:22:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱老师阿鵺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到过去的时间穿越!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了 阿鵺的秘密!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.30,0:22:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美奈子老师 现在的我能用鬼手保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越时空的力量
